<h1  align="center" style="font-size:10vw"> Magic: The Gathering hobby project</h1>

<hr>



<pre>    Magic the Gathering is a table top board
game created in the 1993 by the company Wizards of the 
coasts inc. From just 2008-2016 over 20 billion magic 
cards were printed and as of 2023 the card game has 
approximate 50 million players!</pre>
<pre>  The Goal of this game to build your own 
deck that will play against other peoples and kill 
them as quickly as possible with creatures, magical 
spells, and anyways you can think of, with how many 
cards are out there any play style is possible </pre>

<hr>

<p align="center"> Want to learn more about the cards?<a href="https://squidums08.w3spaces.com/saved-from-Tryit-2024-05-30-u758h.html">Click here!</a>
And if you want to learn to play read this helpful guide!<a href="https://squidums08.w3spaces.com/saved-from-Tryit-2024-05-30-ndou8.html">Click here!</a>
