Page Two Code - How to play

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>How to Play!</title>
<style>
body {
  background-color: AliceBlue;
}

</head>
</style>
<body>

<h1  align="center" style="font-size:10vw">How to Play?</h1>

<hr>

<p1 style="font-size:2.3vw" >Begin your Turn</p1>
<pre style="font-size:2.3vw">
Untap : this means re-set all of your cards by turning them upright signifying they are ready to be used again
Draw : draw a card from your deck you get one per turn <pre>


<br>

<p2 style="font-size:2.3vw" >Main Phase 1</p2>
<pre style="font-size:2.3vw">
Land : put one land from your hand onto the battlefield
Casting : play creatures or other spells you want :) <pre>

<br>

<p3 align="left" style="font-size:2.3vw">Combat Phase</p3>
<pre style="font-size:2.3vw">
Attack! : declare all creature you're attacking with 
block : your opponents declare all creatures they plan to block with
combat damage : now the attackers and blockers fight and you get to see how the combat phase plays out! <pre>

<br>

<p4 style="font-size:2.3vw">Main Phase 2</p4>
<pre style="font-size:2.3vw"> 
Land : play a land if you haven't already 
Casting : cast creatures or spells <pre>

<br>

<p5 style="font-size:2.3vw">End of Turn!</p5>
<pre style="font-size:2.3vw">
Healing : this is when all of your creatures regain their health 
Pass : pass on the turn to the other players in your pod
<pre>

</body>
