<body>

<h1 align="center" style="font-size:10vw">The Cards Themselves</h1>

<hr>

<pre style="font-size:2.3vw">
The game consists of over 27,000 unique cards not
including the many variants of art for each different card.
Millions of cards are printed every year with new cards
being created and released about 3 -4 times a year! In
the new sets they create new cards to continue adding to
the game but also new versions of the art printed on the 
cards. Many sets are of different games and hobbies the 
players enjoy (warhammer 40k, lords of the rings, animes,
street fighter, and fortnite are some common ones).<pre>

</body>
